NK016(ma)010:0: na rag dong sprugs phyag rgya gcig pa'i sgrub thabs zab don nying khu zhes bya bzhugs so //
NK016(ma)010:1: na rag gdong sprugs phyag rgya gcig pa'i sgrub thabs zab don nying khu zhes bya ba /
NK016(ma)010:2: rnam 'gyur srid zhi'i chos kun zag med kyi //
NK016(ma)010:3: lhan skyes bde chen rdo rjera ro mnyam gang //
NK016(ma)010:4: rab 'byams zhi khro'i 'khor lor snang mdzad pa'i //
NK016(ma)010:5: khyab bdag bla mar dngos kun dang bas 'dud //
NK016(ma)010:6: 'dir rnal 'byor spyi'i skong bshags na rag dong sprugs
NK016(ma)010:7: kyi sgrub thabs rdo rje sems dpa' phyag rgya gcig
NK016(ma)010:8: pa'i sgo nas nyams su len par 'dod pas /
NK016(ma)010:9: yid dang mthun zhing shis pa'i gnas su stan bde ba la 'dug ste /
NK016(ma)010:10: thog mar rgyud sbyang ba ni /
NK016(ma)010:11: bla ma rig 'dzin rgyal ba zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor
NK016(ma)010:12: gyi lha tshogs thams cad badz+ra sa m+aa dzah zhes
NK016(ma)010:13: pas mkha' khyab tu sad par mos te /
NK016(ma)010:14: bdag dang mkha' mnyam sems can rnams //
NK016(ma)010:15: rdo rje slob dpon sangs rgyas dpal //
NK016(ma)010:16: dus gsum bzhugs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)010:17: mchog gsum bsten pa'i zhing gyur la //
NK016(ma)010:18: gnyis med yid kyis skyabs su mchi //
NK016(ma)010:19: dngos 'byor yid kyis rnam sprul pa'i //
NK016(ma)010:20: dag pa'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK016(ma)010:21: dngos grub chu bo gcod pa'i gegs //
NK016(ma)010:22: nyes byas ma lus bshags par bgyi //
NK016(ma)010:23: phyogs bcu 'khor gsum dag pa'i chos //
NK016(ma)010:24: ma chags spyod la rjes yi rang //
NK016(ma)010:25: dag pa'i mtha' bzhi dri ma med //
NK016(ma)010:26: rdzogs pa'i byang chub sems bskyed do //
NK016(ma)010:27: bde gshegs byang chub sems dpa' la //
NK016(ma)010:28: dag pa gsum gyi lus dbul lo //
NK016(ma)010:29: tshe rabs bgrangs pa'i las rnams kun //
NK016(ma)010:30: bsdus te byang chub chen por bsngo //
NK016(ma)010:32: tshogs zhing rnams rang la bsdus te /
NK016(ma)010:33: sems nyid nam mkha' lta bu'i ngang la rtsol bral bsal bzhag med par dar cig bzhag go //
NK016(ma)010:36: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK016(ma)010:38: bdag nyid skad cig gis rdo rje he ru ka
NK016(ma)010:39: sku mdog mthing nag rdo rje dang dung khrag 'dzin
NK016(ma)010:40: pa yum dang bcas pa'i skur gyur /
NK016(ma)010:41: h'u h'u h'u bi shwa badz+ra kro d+ha dz+wa la man+da phata phata phata /
NK016(ma)010:42: ha la ha la ha la h'u /
NK016(ma)010:43: zhes brjod pas yab yum gnyis kyi sbyor mtshams nas
NK016(ma)010:44: khro bo 'chol ba mtshon cha sna tshogs kyi char
NK016(ma)010:45: 'bebs pa dpag tu med pa spros /
NK016(ma)010:46: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa tsan+da
NK016(ma)010:47: sarba dush+t+aan+ta ka ha na da ha pa tsa h'u
NK016(ma)010:48: h'u h'u phata / ces bskur bas /
NK016(ma)010:49: khro bo'i tshogs nam mkha' gang ba rnams kyis bgegs thams cad bsdigs bskrad brlag par byas /
NK016(ma)010:50: badz+ra pany+tsa ra ram yam kham /
NK016(ma)010:52: khro bo'i rang bzhin gyi rdo rje'i gur khang chen
NK016(ma)010:53: pos gtams pa'i phyi rol kun tu bskal pa'i me
NK016(ma)010:55: rgya mtsho'i rba rlabs 'khrug pa'i rwa ba gsum rim
NK016(ma)010:56: gyis phyogs kun gang bas mtshams bcad de cis kyang
NK016(ma)010:60: dang po sbyor ba byang chub kyi sems rnam pa gnyis bskyed pa las /
NK016(ma)010:62: bdag dang mtha' yas sems can rnams //
NK016(ma)010:63: ye nas sangs rgyas yin mod kyang //
NK016(ma)010:64: rtog pa'i dbang gis 'khor ba las //
NK016(ma)010:65: byang chub mchog tu sems skyed do //
NK016(ma)010:67: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK016(ma)010:68: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK016(ma)010:69: skye ba med las thams cad skyes //
NK016(ma)010:70: skyes pa nyid na skye ba med //
NK016(ma)010:71: de bzhin du skye ba'i gnas su 'gag pa dang /
NK016(ma)010:75: gnyis pa ting nge 'dzin gyi rim pa la gnyis te /
NK016(ma)010:79: dang po ting nge 'dzin gsum bsgom pa ni /
NK016(ma)010:80: dngos rnams nyid na dngos med pa //
NK016(ma)010:81: rtog pa'i smra bsam yul las 'das //
NK016(ma)010:82: de bzhin nyid dbyings ye shes te //
NK016(ma)010:83: de phyir dngos po dngos med pa'o //
NK016(ma)010:84: 'di ltar snang ba'i chos thams cad mi dmigs shing
NK016(ma)010:85: spros pa dang bral ba stong pa nyid du bsgom
NK016(ma)010:87: de bzhin nyid ni spros med kyang //
NK016(ma)010:88: rang bzhin kun tu snang ba'i dbyings //
NK016(ma)010:89: sems can kun la snying brtse'i phyir //
NK016(ma)010:90: nam mkha' la ni nam mkha' bsgom //
NK016(ma)010:91: de bzhin nyid ma rtogs pa'i sgyu ma lta bu'i
NK016(ma)010:92: sems can rnams la 'dzin med sgyu ma lta bu'i
NK016(ma)010:93: snying rje chen po mkha' khyab tu sgom pa ni
NK016(ma)010:94: kun snang ngo // dngos po med las dngos po'i sprin //
NK016(ma)010:96: gzhi rtsa med pa'i sems nyid ni //
NK016(ma)010:97: chos rnams kun gyi rtsa ba yin //
NK016(ma)010:98: sems nyid yi ge'i rang bzhin te //
NK016(ma)010:99: yi ge yid bzhin rin chen sprin //
NK016(ma)010:100: yi ge mchog ni bsgom par bya //
NK016(ma)010:101: rang rig snang stong gnyis su med pa'i rang bzhin
NK016(ma)010:102: a dkar po'i rnam par bsgom pa ni rgyu'i ting
NK016(ma)010:103: nge 'dzin no // gnyis pa rten dang brten pa'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa ni /
NK016(ma)010:104: sems nyid a dkar po dri ma med par gsal ba las /
NK016(ma)010:105: e yam wam lam sum ram rnams chad /
NK016(ma)010:109: e las nam mkha' chos kyi 'byung gnas 'byams klas pa'i dbyings su /
NK016(ma)010:110: yam las rlung gi dkyil 'khor ljang gu g.yo ba'i ba dan gyis mtshan pa /
NK016(ma)010:111: wam las chu'i dkyil 'khor dkar po zlum po /
NK016(ma)010:112: lam las sa'i dkyil 'khor ser po gru bzhi /
NK016(ma)010:113: sum las rin po che sna bzhi'i rang bzhin gyi ri rab zur bzhi /
NK016(ma)010:114: ram las me'i khor yug nam mkha'i mtha' klas par 'bar ba'o //
NK016(ma)010:115: ri rab kyi steng du rgyu'i a las b+h+ru chad /
NK016(ma)010:116: s+pha ra sam ha b+h+rum bi shwa bi shud+d+he badz+ra dz+ny+aa na tsakra man+da la b+h+rum /
NK016(ma)010:117: b+h+rum yig yongs su gyur pa las /
NK016(ma)010:118: ye shes rin po che 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang /
NK016(ma)010:119: rgya phyogs bcur yongs su ma chad pa /
NK016(ma)010:120: yon tan dpag tu med pa rgyas pa'i spyir gru bzhir gyur pa /
NK016(ma)010:121: lhag pa'i ye shes rin po che'i glo 'bur gyis mdzes pa /
NK016(ma)010:122: rtse mo phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i sangs rgyas kyi dkyil
NK016(ma)010:123: 'khor ma lus pa thams cad so so ma yin
NK016(ma)010:124: zhing ngo bo nyid gcig pa'i ye shes kun tu
NK016(ma)010:125: 'khyil ba / ye shes bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i
NK016(ma)010:126: ye shes rin po che'i dbyibs dang gzhi dang rgyan
NK016(ma)010:128: bkod pa tshad med pas 'phags pa /
NK016(ma)010:129: zag pa med pa'i 'dod yon gyi rnam pa ma
NK016(ma)010:130: tshang ba med pa thams cad kyis nam mkha'i mtha'
NK016(ma)010:131: klas par gang ba'i dbus su /
NK016(ma)010:132: seng ge chen po brgyad kyis btegs pa'i rin po
NK016(ma)010:133: che'i khri bkod pa phul du byung ba'i steng du
NK016(ma)010:137: pad nyi zla ba'i gdan cha shas yongs su rdzogs par gyur /
NK016(ma)010:138: rang gi sems nyid a dkar po dri ma med
NK016(ma)010:139: par gsal ba zla ba'i gdan gyi steng du babs
NK016(ma)010:140: / de yongs su gyur pa las h'u yig mthing ga gsal zhing 'bar ba /
NK016(ma)010:141: s+pha ra de las 'od zer 'phros sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa bsgrubs /
NK016(ma)010:142: sam ha slar 'dus h+au la thim /
NK016(ma)010:143: h'u yongs su gyur pa las /
NK016(ma)010:145: rang nyid bcom ldan 'das dpal rdo rje sems dpa'
NK016(ma)010:146: sku mdog mthing ga in+d+ra n+ai la'i lhun po la
NK016(ma)010:147: nyi ma shar ba ltar 'od zer rab tu 'bar
NK016(ma)010:148: ba / zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
NK016(ma)010:149: zhi zhing rab tu 'dzum pa'i mdangs gsal ba'i zhal
NK016(ma)010:150: gyi 'gyur ba ting nge 'dzin gyis rnam par rol
NK016(ma)010:151: pa'i nyams can / mtshan dang dpe byad kyis 'bar ba /
NK016(ma)010:152: phyag g.yas rdo rje thugs kar 'dzin cing /
NK016(ma)010:153: g.yon dril bu dkur brten pas yum la 'khyud pa /
NK016(ma)010:154: dbu skra ral ba'i thor tshugs can /
NK016(ma)010:155: zhabs gnyis rdzogs pa'i skyil mo krung gis brtan par bzhugs pa'o //
NK016(ma)010:156: yab kyi thugs ka nas m+aum chad /
NK016(ma)010:157: s+pha ra sam ha 'phro 'dus yongs su gyur pa las /
NK016(ma)010:159: yab kyi g.yon phyogs nye ba'i pang du yum rdo
NK016(ma)010:160: rje dbyings phyug ma sngon mo g.yas dril bu 'dzin
NK016(ma)010:162: g.yon rdo rje thugs kar 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)010:163: brtul zhugs kyi skyil mo krung gis 'khril ba /
NK016(ma)010:164: gnyis ka'ang lha rdzas kyi dar dkar po gser gyi ngang ris can gyi stod g.yogs dang /
NK016(ma)010:166: kha dog sna tshogs pa'i cod pan /
NK016(ma)010:168: gar gyi phu rung ste dar gyi chos gos lnga dang /
NK016(ma)010:175: phyag zhabs kyi gdu bu ste rin po che'i rgyan brgyad kyis mdzes par spras pa /
NK016(ma)010:176: mnyen lcugs 'khril ldem gzhon tshul can /
NK016(ma)010:177: gsal 'tsher lhun sdug gzi byin ldan pa ste /
NK016(ma)010:178: zhi ba'i nyams dgu rgyas pa /
NK016(ma)010:179: sangs rgyas kyi sprin phung mtha' yas par 'char ba'i
NK016(ma)010:180: 'od zer kha dog drug gi snang ba re re
NK016(ma)010:181: yang bye ba phrag drug drug tu 'phro zhing 'bar
NK016(ma)010:182: ba'i klong na bde stong gnyis su med pa'i ngo
NK016(ma)010:183: bor bzhugs pa yab yum gnyis ka'i srog gi gor
NK016(ma)010:184: rang dang 'dra ba'i ye shes sems dpa' rgyan dang
NK016(ma)010:185: phyag mtshan spangs pa re re'i thugs kar zla ba
NK016(ma)010:186: la gnas pa'i h'u m+aum gyis mtshan par bsam mo
NK016(ma)010:187: / gsum pa dbang bskur zhing byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK016(ma)010:188: de las 'od zer 'phros pas phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i
NK016(ma)010:189: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad dbang gi lha rigs
NK016(ma)010:190: lnga yab yum gyi rnam par badz+ra sa m+aa dzahs
NK016(ma)010:191: spyan drangs / sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa
NK016(ma)010:192: a nu r+aa ga na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma
NK016(ma)010:193: spyan drangs / ko&a ham / zhes bskul bas /
NK016(ma)010:194: de rnams gnyis su med par sbyor ba mdzad /
NK016(ma)010:195: rjes chags kyi mes zhu ba'i ye shes lnga'i chu
NK016(ma)010:196: rgyun mgo bo'i gnas lngar babs te dbang bskur bar
NK016(ma)010:197: gyur / rdo rje bsdams pa las gung mo gnyis gshibs nas brkyang pa spyi bor bzhag la /
NK016(ma)010:198: mo ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK016(ma)010:199: de bzhin du mdzub mo brkyang ba dpral bar /
NK016(ma)010:200: ma h+aa +aa dar+sha srin lag brkyang pa rna ltag g.yas par /
NK016(ma)010:202: mthe bong brkyang pa ltag par /
NK016(ma)010:203: mo ma h+aa pra t+ya bee k+sha na mthe chung brkyang pa rna ltag g.yon par /
NK016(ma)010:204: ma h+aa kri t+ya nush+th+aa na zhes dbang bskur bas nyon mongs pa lnga'i dri ma sbyangs /
NK016(ma)010:205: phung po lnga rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas su gnas gyur /
NK016(ma)010:206: chu' lhag ma spyi bor brtan pa yongs su gyur
NK016(ma)010:207: pa las mi bskyod pa bdag por gyur pa'i rigs
NK016(ma)010:208: lnga sprul sku'i cha byad can gyis dbu brgyan par
NK016(ma)010:209: bsam la / phung po lnga dag pa rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas su nga rgyal bya'o //
NK016(ma)010:210: de nas byin gyis rlob pa ni /
NK016(ma)010:211: spyi bor zla ba la gnas pa'i dkar po /
NK016(ma)010:212: de'i 'od zer gyis de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs rgyud bskul /
NK016(ma)010:213: sku rdo rje'i lha tshogs nam mkha' gang bar byon /
NK016(ma)010:215: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku dang gnyis su med par gyur /
NK016(ma)010:216: yongs su gyur pa las rnam snang dkar po 'khor lo 'dzin pas rgyas btab par bsam la /
NK016(ma)010:217: rdo rje'i phyag rgya spyi bor gtugs pa /
NK016(ma)010:218: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK016(ma)010:219: mgrin par pad+ma la gnas pa'i +aam dmar po /
NK016(ma)010:220: de'i 'od zer gyis de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs rgyud bskul /
NK016(ma)010:221: gsung rdo rje'i lha tshogs nam mkha' gang bar byon /
NK016(ma)010:223: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi gsung dang gnyis su med par gyur /
NK016(ma)010:224: +aam yongs su gyur pa las snang mtha' dmar po pad+ma 'dzin pas rgyas btab par bsam la /
NK016(ma)010:226: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa w+aa ka badz+ra swa s+b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK016(ma)010:227: snying gar nyi ma la gnas pa'i h'u sngon po /
NK016(ma)010:228: de'i 'od zer gyis de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs rgyud bskul /
NK016(ma)010:229: thugs rdo rje'i lha tshogs nam mkha' gang bar byon /
NK016(ma)010:231: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs dang gnyis su med par gyur /
NK016(ma)010:232: h'u yongs su gyur pa las mi bskyod pa sngon
NK016(ma)010:233: po rdo rje 'dzin pas rgyas btab par bsam la
NK016(ma)010:235: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK016(ma)010:236: zhes rdo rje gsum du nga rgyal bya'o //
NK016(ma)010:237: bzhi pa ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor dang gnyis su med par bya ba la bzhi las /
NK016(ma)010:238: dang po snyan gsan dbab pa ni /
NK016(ma)010:239: rang gi thugs kar dwangs ma'i srog h'u mthing ga
NK016(ma)010:240: ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin rtag tu 'char bzhin pa
NK016(ma)010:241: / de las byung ba'i 'od zer gyis phyogs bcu
NK016(ma)010:242: dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad bskul bas
NK016(ma)010:243: / / chos sku 'gyur ba med pa'i ngang las
NK016(ma)010:244: gzugs sku rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum gyi rnam
NK016(ma)010:246: lag gnyis lcags kyu'i phyag rgya dang bcas pas /
NK016(ma)010:247: h'u stong pa shin tu yod med rnal 'byor mthus //
NK016(ma)010:248: nam mkha' bzhin las dam tshig nye bar gnas //
NK016(ma)010:249: bde bshegs bde bar gshegs mdzad dgongs su gsol //
NK016(ma)010:250: rdo rje sems dpa' khyod bdag skal bzang dpal //
NK016(ma)010:251: ye shes e h+ye tshur byon hi tshur byon b+ha ga w+aan bcom ldan 'das /
NK016(ma)010:252: ma h+aa k+aa ru ni ka /
NK016(ma)010:253: thugs rje chen po dang ldan pa /
NK016(ma)010:255: hoh sa ma ya s+t+wamh dus la bab po gnyis pa spyan drang ba ni //
NK016(ma)010:256: thugs rje lcags kyus thugs dam rgyud bskul zhing //
NK016(ma)010:257: byams pa'i zhags pas gnas nas spyan yang 'dren //
NK016(ma)010:258: lcags sgrog bka' yi pho nya gnas bskyod la //
NK016(ma)010:259: bde gshegs bzhugs shing rnam grol dgyes pa bskyed //
NK016(ma)010:260: dam tshig pa'i thugs ka nas spros pa'i dzahmh'u bam
NK016(ma)010:261: hohs ye shes pa dgug bcings bsdams la dgyes pa
NK016(ma)010:262: skyed nas / dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor dang me ri 'dab 'byor du bzhugs par bsam mo //
NK016(ma)010:263: gsum pa rig pa'i me tog dor ba ni /
NK016(ma)010:265: +aam badz+ra h'u badz+ra s+w+aa badz+ra h+aa badz+ra zhes dor bas /
NK016(ma)010:266: dam tshig pa dang ye shes pa gnyis kyi sku
NK016(ma)010:267: gsung thugs yon tan phrin las rnams gnyis su med
NK016(ma)010:268: par bsam mo // bzhi pa dngos grub bskul zhing bstim pa ni //
NK016(ma)010:269: ye shes rgyal po sku gsung thugs //
NK016(ma)010:270: yon tan phrin las rmad po che //
NK016(ma)010:271: de nyid du ni mnyam sbyor bas //
NK016(ma)010:272: phyag rgya chen por bdag sbyor cig /
NK016(ma)010:274: gnyis su med par bsdus shig /
NK016(ma)010:276: byin gyis rlobs pa'i dus la bab bo //
NK016(ma)010:277: mo badz+ra sa ma ya hoh bdag la mnyes par mdzod cig /
NK016(ma)010:279: dzahmh'u bam hoh zhes phyag rgya bzhis dkyil 'khor gyi
NK016(ma)010:280: 'khor lo chu la chu bzhags pa bzhin dbyer med
NK016(ma)010:282: lnga pa bzlas pa bya ba ni /
NK016(ma)010:283: rang dam tshig sems dpa' rdor sems su gsal ba'i srog gi gor rang 'dra'i ye shes sems dpa' /
NK016(ma)010:284: de'i thugs kar zla ba la ting nge 'dzin sems
NK016(ma)010:285: dpa' h'u yig gi mthar g.yas bskor du yi ge
NK016(ma)010:286: brgya pa'i sngags phreng kha dog dkar po 'od 'bar
NK016(ma)010:287: ba / s+pha ra de las byung ba'i 'od zer
NK016(ma)010:288: gyis phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa sras
NK016(ma)010:289: dang bcas pa thams cad kyi thugs rgyud bskul /
NK016(ma)010:290: bdag dang mkha' khyab kyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi zhal nas sngags kyi sgra dang /
NK016(ma)010:291: thugs rje'i 'od zer 'phros pas khams gsum thams cad snang bar byas /
NK016(ma)010:293: dmigs yul gtso bor gyur pa'i sems can thams cad sangs rgyas kyi zhing du bsgral /
NK016(ma)010:294: sam ha 'od zer rnams slar 'dus te rang la
NK016(ma)010:295: thim pas snod bcud thams cad lha sngags 'od gsal
NK016(ma)010:296: gyi 'khor lor sad par mos la /
NK016(ma)010:297: badz+ra sa t+wa sa ma ya /
NK016(ma)010:298: sogs yig brgya'i dzapa brgya stong la sogs pa ste /
NK016(ma)010:299: tha ma yang nyer gcig las mi nyung bazla'o //
NK016(ma)010:300: yang dgos pa khyad par can gyi slad du las sbyor gyi bzlas pa byed par spro na /
NK016(ma)010:302: da ha da ha sarba na ra ka ga te
NK016(ma)010:303: sogs ngan song sbyong ba'i sngags sbrel ba'ang cung zad
NK016(ma)010:304: re bzla zhing / gnas lung lta bu dang 'brel na phyir zlog gi brab rdzas la basngagasa so //
NK016(ma)010:305: drug pa bsdu zhing ldang ba ni /
NK016(ma)010:306: nyal ba'am mthun sdu ba'i tshe /
NK016(ma)010:307: s+pha ra thugs ka'i h'u yig las 'od zer gyi
NK016(ma)010:308: sprin 'phros pas snod bcud thams cad dag cing 'od
NK016(ma)010:309: gsal bar byas sam ha dag pa'i snod bcud thams
NK016(ma)010:310: cad gzhal yas khang la thim /
NK016(ma)010:311: de dam tshig sems dpa' yab yum la thim /
NK016(ma)010:313: de ye shes sems dpa' la /
NK016(ma)010:314: de ting nge 'dzin sems dpa' h'u la /
NK016(ma)010:315: h'u gyen rdzogs n+aa da'i bar du thim nas rnam
NK016(ma)010:316: par rtog med lhun grub nam mkha' lta bu'i ngang
NK016(ma)010:320: h'u badz+ra d+h+rika ces brjod pas /
NK016(ma)010:321: skad cig gis rang nyid dpal rdo rje sems dpa' snang stong sgyu ma lta bu'i skur langs te /
NK016(ma)010:322: snang grags 'gyu gsum la lha sngags 'od gsal gyi
NK016(ma)010:323: 'khor los rgyas btab nas thun mtshams thams cad don
NK016(ma)010:324: yod par spyad / de yang langs ma thag /
NK016(ma)010:325: de ltar gyur pa'i spyi bor mo /
NK016(ma)010:326: mgrin par +aah snying gar h'u yig gis mtshan par bsam la /
NK016(ma)010:327: spyi bor khu tshur gnyis mdud cing /
NK016(ma)010:328: badz+ra k+aa w+aa tsi rak+sha ham /
NK016(ma)010:330: lus rdo rje'i go chas zhu lugs su g.yogs pas
NK016(ma)010:331: sgo gsum rdo rje gsum dang dbyer mi phyed par
NK016(ma)010:332: bsam zhing / thams cad ma lus sku gsung thugs //
NK016(ma)010:333: sku gsung thugs kyis kun la khyab //
NK016(ma)010:334: ces brjod cing nga rgyal bya /
NK016(ma)010:335: bsngo ba dang shis pa brjod pas mtha' brgyan no //
NK016(ma)010:336: 'di ni yo ga rnam pa gsum gyi sgor zhugs
NK016(ma)010:337: pa'i rnal 'byor pa rnams kyi nyams chag skong zhing
NK016(ma)010:338: rtog sgrib sbyong ba'i spyi khrus rmad du byung ba
NK016(ma)010:339: yin pas na rgyun gyi nyams len la phan phyir
NK016(ma)010:340: bris pa ste / rdo rje sems dpa' bum pa'i dbang gis lus kyi dri ma sbyong ba dang /
NK016(ma)010:341: lha dbang gis dag pa'i snang ba rab 'byams su
NK016(ma)010:342: bstan pa 'tha' brten bzlas lung dang bcas pa'i dbang
NK016(ma)010:343: dang rjes su 'brel ba'i nyams len no //
NK016(ma)010:344: gzhan yang mkha' 'gro'i gtor dbang dang 'brel bar gtan
NK016(ma)010:345: pa med pa'i mchod sbyin la brten nas rang bzhin
NK016(ma)010:346: dbyings kyi mkha' 'gro dang gnyis su med par bya
NK016(ma)010:348: rtsal dbang dang rjes su 'brel bar lhag pa'i ye
NK016(ma)010:349: shes ngos bzung zhing bskyang ba'i gdams pa rnams kyang
NK016(ma)010:350: nyams su len par spro na khrid yig bkol byang
NK016(ma)010:352: yang dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo yongs su rdzogs pa bsgom par mi nus pa'am mi spro ba dag /
NK016(ma)010:353: phyag rgya gcig pa tsam la bsnyen pa byed par 'don na'ang /
NK016(ma)010:354: 'di nyid thun bzhir bcad nas bsgom zhing lha sngags 'od gsal gyi /
NK016(ma)010:356: yig brgya 'bum phrag gsum mam tha ma'ang 'bum phrag
NK016(ma)010:357: gcig kha skong dang bcas pa las mi nyung ba
NK016(ma)010:358: bzla zhing / dus bsnyen ni zla drug ma nas zla gcig gi bar ro //
NK016(ma)010:360: nyer mkho'i cho ga sbyar tshul te /
NK016(ma)010:364: sngon 'gro bsang chu sgrub pa nas mchod rdzas byin
NK016(ma)010:365: rlabs kyi bar dong sprugs kyi cho ga rgyas pa
NK016(ma)010:367: ma khom na srung 'khor 'dir bshad pa dang /
NK016(ma)010:368: bshags pa ye nas mnyam nyid /
NK016(ma)010:369: dam bca' kun tu bzang po'i sho lo ka gcig /
NK016(ma)010:370: mchod pa bsang sbyang byin rlabs ni sngags rnams brjod pa tsam la bsdus kyang rung la /
NK016(ma)010:371: dngos gzhi kun rdzob sems bskyed nas bzlas pa'i bar
NK016(ma)010:372: phyag rgya gcig pa'i rnal 'byor 'dir bstan ltar byas
NK016(ma)010:373: rjes / bum pa bskyed sngags tsam gyis zhi ba rigs lnga bskyed nas /
NK016(ma)010:380: mchod cing bstod de yig brgya bzlas la bzhu brtul bya /
NK016(ma)010:381: de nas gnas lung gi cho ga gzhan 'dra ba
NK016(ma)010:382: las skyabs 'gro'i rjes su 'jug pa rgyas bsdus ji
NK016(ma)010:383: ltar rigs pas dkyil 'khor du bcug nas /
NK016(ma)010:384: ngan song gnas 'dren gyi dbang dang /
NK016(ma)010:385: rdor sems su bskyed pa la ye shes lnga'i dbang dang /
NK016(ma)010:386: sku gsung thugs dbang rnams dkyus ltar ram /
NK016(ma)010:387: bsdu na ye shes lnga dang rdo rje gsum gyis
NK016(ma)010:388: dbang sngags rgya tsam gyis bskur kyang chad pa'i skyon
NK016(ma)010:389: med do // gnyis pa sbyin sreg ni /
NK016(ma)010:390: 'dir nyer mkho rgyugs che ba'i dbang du byas nas zhi ba'i sreg blugs la sbyor te /
NK016(ma)010:391: de yang sngon 'gro rgyas bsdus kyi 'dor len bshad ma thag pa ltar dang /
NK016(ma)010:392: dngos gzhi bdag bskyed phyag rgya gcig pa'i rnal 'byor
NK016(ma)010:393: bzlas pa'i bar byas rjes dkyil 'khor bsdus te thun
NK016(ma)010:394: mtshams kyi lhar langs nas sbyin sreg gi cho ga
NK016(ma)010:395: la 'jug go // de la 'das pa'i me lha'i skabs /
NK016(ma)010:396: dkyil 'khor rgyas pa sgom pa'i lugs la khrom dkrugs dang rigs bsdus gang la brten kyang rung ste /
NK016(ma)010:397: ting 'dzin gsum bsgom na rgyu'i a las sa bon spros te /
NK016(ma)010:398: thab kyi me'i dbus su 'byung ba rim brtsegs nas brtsams te bsgom zhing /
NK016(ma)010:400: 'jig rten pa mchod pa'i mjug gi me lha 'bar ba'i rnam par bsgyur rjes /
NK016(ma)010:401: thab kyi me'i dbus su e las nam mkha' sogs
NK016(ma)010:402: nas bstod pa'i bar bdag mdun gyi khyad par gyi
NK016(ma)010:404: sbyin sreg gi las chog gang la brten pa'i sgos
NK016(ma)010:405: chos phra mo ma gtogs gzhan dkyus ltar bya ba
NK016(ma)010:406: yin zhing / byon zan dang gshegs skyem kyi tshe /
NK016(ma)010:407: badz+ra sa t+wa +aah zhes pa bdun gyis bkang nas /
NK016(ma)010:408: yig brgya spel tshig dang bcas pas 'bul te /
NK016(ma)010:409: rdor sems ni rigs thams cad kyi khyab byed yin
NK016(ma)010:410: pas khyab bya dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo'i sngags kyis
NK016(ma)010:411: dgang pa dang / dbul ba las khyab che ba yin la /
NK016(ma)010:412: de bzhin du rdzas gzhan rnams la'ang bcu tshan re
NK016(ma)010:413: re'i thog mar yig brgya tshar re brjod pas 'go
NK016(ma)010:414: drangs nas rdzas sngags so sos 'bul lo //
NK016(ma)010:415: ro sreg lta bu'i tshe spro na rdzas rdzogs rjes
NK016(ma)010:416: zhun mar gyi skong dag gyur dang bcas pa'ang mdzad
NK016(ma)010:417: cing / sbyin sreg gang gi tshe yang tshogs mchod 'grub na bya ste /
NK016(ma)010:418: ma 'grub na'ang chad pa'i skyon med do //
NK016(ma)010:419: gal te 'das pa'i me lha yang phyag rgya gcig
NK016(ma)010:420: pa la brten par spro na sbyar bas chog ste
NK016(ma)010:421: / de'i tshul ni bshad ma thag pa'i 'gros kyis shes mod /
NK016(ma)010:422: de ltar na'ang mchod pa rgyas bsdus ji lta rigs
NK016(ma)010:423: pas 'khor ba kun grol lta bu nas blangs rjes
NK016(ma)010:424: / mi rtog rdo rjes bstod pa tsam khyad par ro //
NK016(ma)010:425: de ltar na rag dong sprugs phyag rgya gcig pa'i
NK016(ma)010:426: sgo nas nyams su len tshul 'di nyid lha kun
NK016(ma)010:427: bzang la sbyar yang mi 'gal mod /
NK016(ma)010:428: 'dir ni rigs thams cad kyi khyab byed rdo rje sems dpa' la sbyar ba yin zhing /
NK016(ma)010:429: bshags rgyud kyi dpe phal che bar /
NK016(ma)010:430: gdan yang byang chub sems dpa' brgyad glang po cher sprul pa brgyad kyis /
NK016(ma)010:433: seng ger sprul pa brgyad kyis zhes mi 'dra ba
NK016(ma)010:434: gnyis byung ba gang dag kha tshon chod dka' na'ang
NK016(ma)010:435: / 'dir brgyud pa'i man ngag dbang btsan du byas nas gdan seng ger byas pa yin la /
NK016(ma)010:436: zhabs kyi bzhugs tshul yang man ngag las rdzogs skyil du gsungs pa ltar bkod pa ste /
NK016(ma)010:437: de la bshags rgyud du sems dpa'i skyil mo krung du bzhugs pa /
NK016(ma)010:438: zhes 'byung ba dang 'gal lam snyam na mi 'gal te /
NK016(ma)010:439: sgyu 'phrul mkhan po rnams zhabs g.yas dang g.yon gang
NK016(ma)010:440: rigs cung zad brkyang pa'i phyed skyil la sems skyil
NK016(ma)010:441: du mdzad nas / long bu gnyis mdud pa'i yongs
NK016(ma)010:442: grags kyi sems skyil la rdzogs pa'i skyil krung zhes
NK016(ma)010:443: tha snyad 'dogs pa'i gnad kyis don la 'dra ba
NK016(ma)010:444: du mdzad nas / yin no // ngag tshig 'di la byis blo'i dbang gyur pa'i //
NK016(ma)010:445: nyes kun chos kyi spyan ldan rnams la bshags //
NK016(ma)010:446: legs cha'i dge ba nyin byed dapala 'bar bas //
NK016(ma)010:447: sgrib gnyis mun pa'i dpung tshogs mthar byed shog /
NK016(ma)010:448: ces pa 'di yang rje btsun bla ma dam pa
NK016(ma)010:449: bka' drin mtshungs med gter chen chos kyi rgyal po'i
NK016(ma)010:450: bka'i gnang ba legs par thob pa la brten nas
NK016(ma)010:451: / gang gi bka' drin kho nas 'tsho ba'i gnyos
NK016(ma)010:452: btsun d+harma sh+r+ais chu lug nag zla'i chos brgyad kyi
NK016(ma)010:453: nyin mo stan thog gcig la rdzogs par spel ba'o
